data.description: Beautiful and Move in Ready.  This 3 bedroom, 3 full bath contemporary home has been meticulously maintained and ready for you to call Home.  Open Living concept with a vaulted Living room and Gas Fireplace, Modern kitchen with granite countertops, newer appliances, plenty of storage and a oversized Breakfast Bar with 4 stools.  The Dining room is perfect for formal or everyday dining.  The two Bedrooms on the first floor consist of the owners suite with a large closet and on suite with a walk in shower, and the second bedroom currently being used as an office.  First floor laundry room.  The upper level has a beautiful open loft overlooking the living room and kitchen along with another bedroom and full bathroom.  Sliders to the back patio overlook the spacious back private back yard complete with an oversized $20K shed.  2 car attached garage.  So much to offer in this beautiful home in the private Fox Hollow Development within close proximity of shopping, restaurants, schools, and beautiful downtown Garrettsville.  James A Garfield Local Schools.
